Package: LegitXMut
Type: Package
Title: LegitXMut is designed to handle Nanopore sequencing data in order to perform sequence alignments,
 identify/filter mutation and genomics characteristics, data quality control,
 and calculate&summarize error rates, this package also includes methods for 
 creating comprehensive summary tables and visualizing error distributions and mutation patterns
Version: 0.1.0
